## F8 Sprint 1 — Complete

### What was implemented

**`src/lib/schema-cache.ts`** — TTL-based in-memory cache (60 s) with three exports:
- `getCachedSchema()` — returns cached value if within TTL, else `null`
- `setCachedSchema(value)` — stores with current timestamp
- `invalidateSchemaCache()` — clears cache (used in tests and future invalidation hooks)

**`src/app/api/schema/route.ts`** — `GET /api/schema` handler that:
1. Checks cache first; returns immediately on hit
2. Runs a single ClickHouse query sampling the last 10,000 events using `ARRAY JOIN arrayJoin(JSONExtractKeys(properties))` to expand property keys, then `maxIf(1, JSONExtractFloat(...) != 0)` to detect numeric types
3. Groups results into the spec response shape in application code
4. Caches for 60 s

